How to reach Vasuki Tal?

First reach Kedarnath.
Stay one extra day at Kedarnath if you don’t have any prior experience to 16000ft. Acclimitise your body.

Vasuki is 9km from Kedarnath, 7 km steep ascend to Jai-Vijay Dhar and 2km descend to the lake.

You will pass through the meadows, moraine land and what not!

Try to leave early in the morning from Kedarnath and get back on the same day. 

Hope the videos helps. 

Share and Save with your friends. 😊🙏
